  ('social-worker-moex-01941', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '我們常聽到基層工作人員抱怨主管是「外行人領導內行人」的說法。此說凸顯了主管缺乏何種管理技能？', '["概念性技能（conceptual skill）", "技術性技能（technical skill）", "人群關係技能（human relationship skill）", "政治性技能（political skill）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01942', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下有關Skidmore等人對領導的六項權力（power）來源敘述，何者錯誤？', '["某位社工督導發揮專業才能，總能獲得同仁的敬重，是屬於參考的權力", "某社工的業務表現不佳，因而遭到處罰，是屬於強制權力", "專業發展使然，地方政府社會處長必然擁有專家的權力", "社工科長拔擢績優社工，提升為社工督導，須具備合法權力"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01943', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關領導理論行為模式派別的敘述，何者正確？', '["強調領導者能力、成就、責任屬於「行為論」", "強調工作、關係的權變理論屬於「特質論」", "強調民主式、權威式、放任式領導論述，屬於「情境論」", "強調酬賞激發績效、懲罰不良表現，屬於「當代新領導觀點」下的交易領導"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01944', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '新進社工表現優異，主管擬破例拔擢他升任社工督導。他雖然感到高興，但是隨即想到原本單位的督導， 常常以辦公室為家，幾乎沒有自己的生活品質可言，因而陷入兩難困境，不曉得該如何面對與抉擇。這 是下列何種衝突？', '["雙趨衝突", "雙避衝突", "趨避衝突", "多重趨避衝突"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01945', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關當代新近領導觀點的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["「只要老闆要我做的，赴湯蹈火，在所不辭」是魅力型領導所激發出來的力量", "「領導者能夠描繪出可改善現況的、務實的、吸引人的輪廓」是願景型領導", "「有如早期社會交換理論」的是交易型領導", "從「以老闆為中心」到「以員工為中心」是組織文化模式領導理論的概念"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01946', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '新一代管理大師Peter M. Senge致力於「學習型組織」概念，其對於組織概念主張，以下何者錯誤？', '["以效率為核心架構", "主要概念在於解決問題", "應扁平化", "不斷自我組織再造"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01947', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '組織設計指的是藉由組織的各項活動（activity）將組織使命（mission）、方案宗旨（goal）及方案標的 （objective）串連成具一致努力方向的組織管理工作。試問這四者間的順序關係為何？', '["組織使命→方案宗旨→方案標的→活動", "組織使命→活動→方案宗旨→方案標的", "組織使命→活動→方案標的→方案宗旨", "組織使命→方案宗旨→活動→方案標的"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01948', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關機械型結構（mechanistic structure）組織的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["在於穩定秩序", "強調個人適任專業", "成員分工、角色明確", "容易淡化員工個別的努力成果"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01949', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '好的社會服務方案在目標陳述上，一定要清晰明確，並在行為層次上使用能使情境產生可觀測變化的動 詞來表示。以下用詞何者比較不適合用在目標陳述上？', '["減輕", "改善", "體認", "強化"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01950', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '就執行方案評估（assessment）或評鑑（evaluation）作業的時間點而言，下列方法何者錯誤？', '["形成性評估（formative assessment）", "過程評鑑（process evaluation）", "總結性評鑑（summative evaluation）", "個案評量（case assessment）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
